    T - the type of the components
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.NavigableSet<T>, java.util.Set<T>, java.util.SortedSet<T>

    StateSet, TransitionSet

    public class GraphicComponentSet<T extends GraphicComponent>
extends java.util.TreeSet<T>
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A GraphicComponentSet is an ordered set. The components in this set are ordered ascendantly by their IDs.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
